descriptions.description: Autistic girl Tally navigates new social challenges on a school trip, questioning whether to conform or stand up for herself and others.
Through a freak accident, a modern chemist is transported to planet Anyar, where he must help a pre-industrial society resist conquest by the militant Narthani empire.
A beautiful journal with gold foil embellishments, embossing, and gray lines for writing. Perfect for personal reflection, sketching, or jotting down favorite quotes or poems.
A mesmerizing journal inviting you to immerse yourself in an enchanting undersea world, capturing your thoughts amidst vibrant marine life.
A comprehensive first grade workbook with 300+ engaging activities covering math, reading, phonics, and problem-solving skills for ages 6-7.
A harrowing tale of Rick Grimes' group surviving the zombie apocalypse, facing devastating losses and finding fleeting refuge, forcing them to truly embrace life.
As vampire queen, Betsy faces workplace drama at her nightclub after killing the previous boss. Her life gets complicated when she learns she has a half-sister who's the devil's daughter.
